=== week_1_thursday ===
~ story_date = "Thu. Aug. 30, 2001"
# Evening
# Home - Yahoo! Messenger

The modem screams, then settles into that grainy dial-up hush.
Your buddy list flickers online.

You notice Alex's screen name for half a second before it disappears.
Away already. Or maybe invisible.

Chloe pings you first.

